85
00:05:49,960 --> 00:05:51,200
Then do you remember

86
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:53,880
the lady who sold rice cakes?

87
00:05:53,880 --> 00:05:55,560
♪If we fall in love again♪

88
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:58,480
I remember.

89
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:01,320
She's old.

90
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:05,360
Do you think

91
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:08,600
she's still alive?

92
00:06:21,840 --> 00:06:22,720
Sorry, Your Highness,

93
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:24,800
Xiao Chuyi rescued Lu Yunxi.

94
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:27,320
Useless.

95
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:30,800
You can't even handle a poisoned man.

96
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:33,480
