97
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:03,880
General!

98
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:05,640
Call Doctor Wu.

99
00:07:09,520 --> 00:07:10,360
My Lady.

100
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:16,000
My Lady!

101
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,080
Where are you going?

102
00:07:20,080 --> 00:07:20,920
Prison.

103
00:07:20,960 --> 00:07:21,800
My Lady,

104
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:23,160
you don't have to do this.

105
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:25,640
General Xiao will clear your name.

106
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,600
You can hide in the barrack
for a few days.

107
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:28,920
No one can get in

108
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:29,920
without General Xiao's token.

109
00:07:33,080 --> 00:07:34,520
Take care of him.

110
00:07:37,520 --> 00:07:38,360
My Lady!

111
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:58,640
(Chuyi.)

112
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:03,600
(I've never forgotten
what the Zhous did to our family.)

113
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:07,120
(However, I'm afraid)

114
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:11,240
(we can't go back in time.)

115
00:08:30,760 --> 00:08:31,600
Your Highness!

116
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:33,760
The Purification Poison from Wujiang

117
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:34,680
was intercepted.

118
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:36,680
Doctor Wu.

119
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:41,910
He shouldn't have fought.

120
00:08:42,090 --> 00:08:43,700
Now the poison is in his bones.

121
00:08:43,880 --> 00:08:45,440
If we can't get it out in three days,

122
00:08:45,560 --> 00:08:46,800
even God

123
00:08:46,800 --> 00:08:47,890
can't save him.

124
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:49,040
Answer me.

125
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:50,680
Is fighting poison with poison

126
00:08:50,680 --> 00:08:51,560
the only method?

127
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:53,640
I once knew

128
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:56,440
an exceptional doctor

129
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:58,680
who could cure all kinds of poison.

130
00:08:58,680 --> 00:08:59,800
Unfortunately,

131
00:08:59,800 --> 00:09:01,800
she was sentenced to death
many years ago.

132
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:22,360
Great carbonized hair.

133
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:23,920
You're back.

134
00:09:24,800 --> 00:09:25,640
Are you

135
00:09:27,040 --> 00:09:28,240
Court Lady Chang?

136
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:34,760
You're young.

137
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:36,400
How do you know me?

138
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:39,960
Auntie,

139
00:09:41,920 --> 00:09:43,400
I'm Lu Yunxi, Xiao Chuyi's wife.

140
00:09:43,400 --> 00:09:44,600
I came here for the cure.

141
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,320
Auntie, please help me.

142
00:09:47,280 --> 00:09:48,800
The cure?

143
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:59,440
The cure!

144
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:02,640
If you want the cure,

145
00:10:03,640 --> 00:10:06,080
you'll have to pay the price.

146
00:10:22,880 --> 00:10:24,200
Please tell His Majesty I need

147
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:25,560
(The Golden Mean)
to see him.

148
00:10:25,560 --> 00:10:26,400
My Lord,

149
00:10:26,620 --> 00:10:28,720
the traitors of the Xiaojie Army
broke into the prison

150
00:10:28,850 --> 00:10:30,160
and kidnapped Lady Lu last night.

151
00:10:33,400 --> 00:10:34,240
My Lord, calm down.

152
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:36,000
General Xiao saved her

153
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:36,920
and sent her back.

154
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,440
He also reported to His Majesty

155
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:41,040
that he replaced the drug she gave him
and pretended

156
00:10:41,040 --> 00:10:42,040
to be poisoned

157
00:10:42,040 --> 00:10:43,440
to lure the traitors.

158
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:45,740
His Majesty has ordered them
to release her.

159
00:10:49,760 --> 00:10:50,960
Long live the emperor.

160
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:55,120
His Majesty knew
you knelt for an entire day and

161
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:56,160
didn't eat anything,

162
00:10:56,520 --> 00:10:58,600
so he allowed you
to go home by carriage.

163
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:01,640
That's very kind of His Majesty.

164
00:11:09,400 --> 00:11:10,520
Get the finest Healing Powder.

165
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:11,840
I'll pick Yun up.

166
00:11:13,520 --> 00:11:14,360
General,

167
00:11:14,370 --> 00:11:15,320
