169
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:32,440
I have a favor to ask.

170
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:35,520
Is the Grand Tutor
asking me for a favor?

171
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:39,920
It's about Yunxi.

172
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:41,560
I have no choice.

173
00:11:41,560 --> 00:11:42,400
What happened to her?

174
00:11:44,680 --> 00:11:46,040
Cousin, haven't you noticed

175
00:11:46,600 --> 00:11:47,920
that someone doesn't want her

176
00:11:47,920 --> 00:11:48,840
to get out alive?

177
00:11:51,800 --> 00:11:52,960
Pick Yunxi up first

178
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:54,520
and send her home tomorrow.

179
00:11:56,680 --> 00:11:57,520
I'll talk to

180
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:58,720
